{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/board-game-chips-heroes-uprising/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"CIAYO Games Kenalkan Board Game CHIPS: Heroes Uprising Untuk Lengkapi Game Mobile-nya!","content":"<p>CIAYO Comics dan CIAYO Games datang meramaikan pagelaran <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/bekraf-game-prime-dari-tahun-ke-tahun/\">BEKRAF Game Prime 2018</a>. Jika CIAYO Comics tampil meriah dengan <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-prime-2018-ciayo-comics/\"><em>booth</em> konsep sekolah</a>-nya, CIAYO Games mengusung konsep <em>booth</em> minimalis namun terasa sangat lapang dimana pengunjung bisa bermain games dengan leluasa.</p>\n<p>CIAYO Games memperkenalkan judul game terbaru mereka di Game Prime 2018, yaitu <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/chips-heroes-uprising-tower-game/\">CHIPS: Heroes Uprising</a>. Dalam game <em>mobile</em> ini, Chips harus membangun berbagai <em>tower</em> pertahanan untuk menghalau serangan alien dan menyelamatkan teman-temannya serta seluruh penghuni Chammyland.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49158\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49158\" data-attachment-id=\"49158\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/board-game-chips-heroes-uprising/attachment/01-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-49158\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg\" alt=\"board game chips: heroes uprising\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49158\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Duniaku</p></div></p>\n<p>Kerennya, CIAYO Games nggak hanya membawa game <em>mobile</em> CHIPS: Heroes Uprising, tetapi mereka juga punya <em>board game</em> CHIPS: Heroes Uprising! <em>Board game</em> ini punya setting cerita yang sama dengan game <em>mobile</em>-nya. Hanya saja, tujuan dari <em>board game</em> ini adalah persaingan antara kelompok <em>survivor</em>. Siapakah yang bisa bertahan hidup lebih lama?</p>\n<p>Dalam <em>board game</em> CHIPS: Heroes Uprising, setiap pemain diwajibkan untuk membangun tempat perlindungan, sekaligus menyerang <em>survivor</em> lain. Untuk melindungi diri, pemain bisa menyiapkan perangkap untuk menjebak <em>survivor</em> yang menyerang.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49159\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49159\" data-attachment-id=\"49159\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/board-game-chips-heroes-uprising/attachment/02-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-49159\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Duniaku\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49159\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Duniaku</p></div></p>\n<p>Pemain mulai dengan satu ruangan <em>lobby</em> yang akan menjadi pondasi untuk mengembangkan bangunan perlindungan. Di awal setiap <em>turn</em>, pemain akan mendapatkan uang koin yang disebut <em>caps</em>, sesuai dengan jumlah dan jenis ruangan yang dia punya. Pemain juga bakal mendapatkan dua kartu <em>action</em>. Di setiap <em>turn</em>, pemain bisa melakukan maksimal 3 aksi berbeda: membuat ruangan baru, menyiapkan perangkap, menyerang lawan, menggunakan kartu <em>action</em>, atau melakukan <em>discard</em> kartu.</p>\n<p>Untuk menyerang ruangan lawan, pemain harus menggunakan kartu <em>action</em>, kemudian mengocok dadu untuk menentukan ruangan mana yang diserang. Jika angkanya tidak ada yang cocok berarti serangan meleset. Oh ya, ruangan <em>lobby</em> hanya bisa diserang jika tidak ada ruangan lain yang tersisa pada lawan. Pemain pun baru bisa menyerang lawan di <em>turn</em> ke-2, sehingga pemain bisa memanfaatkan <em>turn</em> pertama untuk membangun pertahanan.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49160\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49160\" data-attachment-id=\"49160\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/board-game-chips-heroes-uprising/attachment/03-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-49160\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Duniaku\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49160\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Duniaku</p></div></p>\n<p>Kembali ke penyerangan, jika angka dalam dadu cocok dengan angka dari ruangan, maka serangan akan dimulai. Pemain harus membandingkan nilai serangan kartu <em>action</em> dengan nilai pertahanan ruangan ditambah nilai pertahanan perangkap (jika ada perangkap). Jika nilai serangan pemain lebih rendah, maka serangan tidak berhasil. Namun jika nilainya melampaui pertahanan, maka ruangan akan hancur dan kamu mendapatkan <em>caps</em> jarahan.</p>\n<p>Pemenang ditentukan oleh peraih <em>victory point</em> terbanyak. <em>Victory point</em>Â dihitung dari jumlah ruangan yang tersisa di akhir permainan.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49208\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49208\" data-attachment-id=\"49208\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/board-game-chips-heroes-uprising/attachment/05-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-49208\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Pictures\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49208\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div></p>\n<p>Nggak sempat main <em>board game</em> CHIPS: Heroes Uprising di Game Prime 2018 kemarin? Tenang, karena CHIPS: Heroes Uprising akan segera rilis di tahun 2018 ini. Sementara itu, game <em>mobile</em> CHIPS: Heroes Uprising akan segera meluncur ke Apple App Store dan Google Play dalam waktu dekat, bersamaan dengan <em>board game</em>-nya. Gimana, tertantang untuk jago main CHIPS: Heroes Uprising versi game <em>mobile</em> dan juga versi <em>board game?</em></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"41f7c697-714e-54a7-9b71-088372924328"}}}